gov.ornl.keva.core

Class UnionIterator<E>

  • java.lang.Object
    • gov.ornl.keva.core.UnionIterator<E>
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.util.Iterator<E>

    public class UnionIterator<E>
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.util.Iterator<E>
    Merge multiple, sorted iterators into a single iterator. This iterator returns values in sorted order across iterators assuming that the user supplies a comparator. This iterator is also special in that users can define equivalence classes. Values within a single equivalence class can be "merged" so that only a single value is returned.
    Author:
    James Horey
